&kp LCTRL      &trans                &kp LA(LC(LG(UP_ARROW)))  &trans                 &kp C_MUTE    &trans        &trans    &kp UP          &trans           &kp TAB
&trans         &kp LA(RC(RG(LEFT)))  &kp LA(LC(LG(DOWN)))      &kp LA(LC(LG(RIGHT)))  &trans        &trans        &kp LEFT  &kp DOWN_ARROW  &kp RIGHT_ARROW  &kp ENTER
                                     &trans                                                                                 &trans
